{"type": "article", "id": 21696, "title": "FOOD-SAUNA（唐小蒸） by 唐恩设计", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-02T07:34:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 67, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115820SG0mNCOAdkMguPwn.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一款快速蒸锅，由唐恩(北京)科技有限公司设计并获得了 2015 年红点奖。团队成员来自清华大学，他们做了一系列厨卫产品，包括能把油烟锁住的空气墙“唐小吹”，能做土灶饭的“唐小煲”，以及这款 6 秒可达到 110 度蒸汽的“唐小蒸”。它的操作也很简单，是折叠式的，打开后放上需要加热的食物并加水就可以实现快速蒸热，比微波炉有更好的口感，是一款试图替代微波炉的产品。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115818qyUDHG9tnbxIQXhV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.46\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115818AX6SPcHYrlDqetNm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115819xjQl18UScziawvbs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115819Eh9G8qHljuASLv50.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}